                <p>A <foreign xml:lang="gez">mawaddǝs</foreign>-type <foreign xml:lang="gez">qǝne</foreign> 
                    that is attributed to <persName cert="high" corresp="SD" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS14574GabraLeul">Gabra Lǝʿul</persName> 
                    in the manuscript <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/UppQ1524o">Uppsala, Uppsala University Library, Q 15:24 o</ref>. It is found also in the older manuscript <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BNFabb145">Paris, Bibliothèque nationale de France d'Abbadie 145</ref>,
                    with no indication to the type and author, but with a few minor differences.</p>
